Subject: [PATCH] Exp 3 iterate: stronger TermSurf dock padding (scale 0.72)

Raise dock_content_scale from 0.89 to 0.72 (~65% mark width, ~17% L/R
plate pad) after operator rejected ~10% sides on the macOS squircle.
